{"tid":1718820,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"我對唔住中大班細路","createTime":"2019-11-14T02:47:16.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-14T02:53:34.000Z","uid":317431,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"cd8f4704b881e5bf48fc8c091249ded082b80385","tid":1718820,"uid":317431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T02:47:16.000Z","msg":"對唔住，我地之前冇好好守住香港<br />\n結果，留低左筆蘇州屎俾你地<br />\n對唔住，我勸唔到，我班廢老同事罷工<br />\n結果，呢兩日令你地受傷<br />\n作為大人，我慚愧，我地冇你地咁勇敢<br />\n但係，我想同呢兩日，所有前線後勤既中大細路你地講<br />\n我為你地自豪，好佩服你地<br />\n從你地身上，我睇到香港未來既希望<br />\n你地第日若果想要咩，出聲就得，<br />\n我地一定會貨金去幫你<br />\n最後，想對班香港大人講<br />\n一定要供你個仔女入中大！<br />\n因為香港只有一大。"},{"pid":"bc928998c4c1e3697947a7f22d91ed52eb9173b7","tid":1718820,"uid":312125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T02:48:48.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">［文宣入！］返工搭鐵受襲、催淚彈影響健康、女學生返學俾狗捉，<strong>請文宣製圖向怕死嘅打工仔、家長、學生宣傳三罷</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n林鄭連續兩日叫大家唔好罷工罷課，證明罷工罷課係佢春袋，然而差佬不斷製造罷工罷課條件，文宣請行動<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n請文宣組以<span style=\"color: red;\">黑警返工時間突襲旺角站無差別襲擊勤力返工人士</span>、<span style=\"color: gold;\">中午中環射催淚彈</span>、<span style=\"color: red;\">警察街上捉返學嘅女學生</span>、<span style=\"color: gold;\">以及警察話上堂等於非法集結</span>，做罷工罷課文宣圖<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">警告堅持要返工返學嘅人，即將面對惡犬強姦殺人滅口嘅危險，在網上廣傳！</span><br />\n<blockquote> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8oPyZO5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8oPyZO5.jpg&h=3f965005&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FJQN4pc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFJQN4pc.jpg&h=87289d57&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/abpOQ16.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FabpOQ16.png&h=1a9ab24c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zQHwOww.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzQHwOww.jpg&h=056adf34&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JerhLyH.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJerhLyH.png&h=a8e9db0f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n</blockquote><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1713400\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1713400</a>"},{"pid":"4a86377fe32646bb51071c5676f5cff72de9774e","tid":1718820,"uid":313764,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T02:48:56.000Z","msg":"香港唔係得中大有做緊野<br />\n支持還支持 唔好比人有分化既機會"},{"pid":"e121aff43c300571961580c272c36fc0381db2e1","tid":1718820,"uid":311566,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T02:51:46.000Z","msg":"師兄，香港唔係剩係得暴大，你望下隔離嘅poly,city,kongu,bu,有邊間唔係打緊？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />根本間間都值得入<br />\n利申暴大"},{"pid":"bcefd91ebcb0cb0fb48fbf9417c4df3632779485","tid":1718820,"uid":337761,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T02:53:34.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">連登嘅冷氣軍師，想幫手又冇得發夢嘅，</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">唔該幫手上Twitter，Reddit幫手！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">前線搏晒老命同班警甴對抗，</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">你哋唔係連撳幾個掣都懶呀嘛？</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">Retweet + Like + Reply</span></span><br />\n－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－<br />\n美國議員繼續為香港發聲，大家快啲去回應支持啦～<br />\n<br />\n！！！提出法案嘅Marco Rubio話有好消息！！！<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/marcorubio/status/1194749198345949187\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fmarcorubio%2Fstatus%2F1194749198345949187&d=Ue9aQsdn%2FMYV7LryoIv%2BZOxpY9ERoCMedVnvBBvIoB8%3D&h=c5bafa4f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fmarcorubio%2Fstatus%2F1194749198345949187&h=c1718001\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/marcorubio/status